query:
SELECT e.id, e.name, et.targetType, et.targetValue, et.currentValue, et.baseValue, et.month, et.year 
FROM employees e 
LEFT JOIN employee_targets et ON e.id = et.employeeId 
WHERE e.name LIKE '%غادة%' AND et.month = 1 AND et.year = 2026;
